---
title: Crispy Shallot-Topped Chicken with Roasted Veggies and Gravy
description: This simple but decadent dish is packed with layers of flavour and texture! Tender chicken thighs are smothered in a creamy gravy and topped with crunchy, crispy shallots. Roasted carrots and zucchini round out the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-garni-dechalotes-frites-9687106e.jpg
